==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Interviewing
<hw>In"ter*view`ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The act or custom of
holding an interview or interviews.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>An article on <qex>interviewing</qex> in the ⟦ldquo⟧Nation⟦rdquo⟧
of January 28, 1869, . . . was the first formal notice of the practice
under that name.</q> <rj><qau>The American.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

